sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Customer
    participant Ctrl as PaymentV1Controller
    participant PF as PaymentFacade
    participant OS as OrderService
    participant PS as PaymentService
    participant PG as PgClient (RestTemplate)
    participant Sim as pg-simulator (외부)

    C->>Ctrl: 결제 요청 (POST /api/v1/payments)
    Note over Ctrl: @LoginMember 인증

    activate PF
    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note right of PF: @Transactional
        PF->>OS: getOrder(orderId, userId)
        OS-->>PF: OrderModel (상태: CREATED)
        PF->>PF: order.startPayment()
        Note over PF: 주문 상태 → PAYMENT_PENDING

        PF->>PF: PaymentModel 생성 (PENDING)
        Note over PF: maskedCardNo, order.finalAmount()
        PF->>PS: save(payment)
        PS-->>PF: PaymentModel (id 채번)

        PF->>PG: requestPayment(pgRequest, userId)
        Note over PG: X-USER-ID 헤더 설정
        PG->>Sim: POST /api/v1/payments
        Note over Sim: 요청 지연: 100ms~500ms<br/>성공률: 60%

        alt PG 요청 성공
            Sim-->>PG: {transactionKey, status: PENDING}
            PG-->>PF: PgPaymentResponse
            PF->>PF: payment.assignTransactionKey(txKey)
        else PG 요청 실패 / 타임아웃
            Sim-->>PG: 에러 또는 타임아웃
            PG-->>PF: Exception
            PF-->>C: PG_REQUEST_FAILED (502)
            Note over PF: 트랜잭션 롤백<br/>주문 상태 CREATED로 복원
        end
    end
    deactivate PF

    PF-->>C: 200 OK {paymentId, transactionKey, status: PENDING}

    Note over Sim: 비동기 처리 (1s~5s)
    Note over Sim: 성공 70% / 한도초과 20% / 잘못된카드 10%
